OL,3,CFirefighter honoured with Elizabeth
OL,4,CEmblem 28 years after her death
OL,6,FHome Secretary, Yvette Cooper said:
OL,7,F"We will forever remember the heroism
OL,8,Fof these police officers, firefighters
OL,9,Fand public servants, whose acts of
OL,10,Fselfless courage provide an example to
OL,11,Fus all. Like Her Majesty Queen
OL,12,FElizabeth II, they dedicated their
OL,13,Flives to the service of their
OL,14,Fcommunities, and it is fitting that we
OL,15,Fthank them and honour them with the
OL,16,FEmblem created in her name.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
